                                                    <li>4.2 You can also place a request for return of any product by calling the customer support at 9430270997.</li><br>
                                                    <li>4.3 After your return request is processed, you wiil be notified for the same via, email/whatsapp. You would be advised to pack the item as delivered to you and ship them to the address of the sender via speed post/courier.  The cost for the same will be credited to your wallet in your profile.</li><br>
                                                    <li>C.  Refund Policy</li><br>
